{
  "id": "RAW_015124",
  "title": "智元机器人发布并开源首个机器人动作序列驱动的世界模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651245474&idx=3&sn=dce595851fb6d67e96ea2792b4fb1dd7",
  "date": "2025-05-24 02:16:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b7dded31-9be4-4349-d1df-dbe6ecc97700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"90\" data-imgfileid=\"503629017\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b7dded31-9be4-4349-d1df-dbe6ecc97700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">作者 | 褚杏娟 </span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">近日，智元机器人重磅发布具身智能领域双重里程碑式突破：全球首个基于机器人动作序列驱动的具身世界模型 EVAC (EnerVerse-AC)，以及具身世界模型评测基准 EWMBench。这两大创新成果现已全面开源，旨在构建“低成本模拟 - 标准化评测 - 高效迭代”的全新开发范式，持续赋能全球具身智能研究，加速技术落地与产业发展。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">EVAC arxiv：https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.09723</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">EVAC 开源代码：https://github.com/AgibotTech/EnerVerse-AC</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">EWMBench arxiv: https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.09694</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">EWMBench 开源代码：https://github.com/AgibotTech/EWMBench</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前具身智能演进面临两大关键制约：在测试阶段，真机验证代价大、风险高，仿真系统又受制于虚实偏差；在数据层面，海量真机数据尚未构建基于轨迹扩增的高效利用机制，限制了多样性生成与泛化训练。为打破困局，智元机器人在去年发布的世界模型架构 EnerVerse 基础上推出创新成果：基于动作序列驱动的世界模型 EVAC 与具身世界模型评测榜单 EWMBench，构建从训练到评测全链路技术闭环，重新定义具身世界模型研发范式。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/313e2e4c-d404-46e9-1145-eaf024e34100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">全球首个机器人动作序列驱动的世界模型</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EVAC 是一个能够动态复现机器人与环境复杂交互的世界模型，标志着从传统仿真到生成式模拟的跃迁。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/665af0ce-0a00-495f-d32b-4753f2d7d600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5531400966183575\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503761796\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/665af0ce-0a00-495f-d32b-4753f2d7d600/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfe9f80e-6c39-4a47-f419-14a51e7cb700/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">核心能力：从 “物理执行” 到“像素空间”的精准映射</span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EVAC 基于前序工作 EnerVerse 架构持续演进，创新型引入多级动作条件注入机制，实现 “物理动作 - 视觉动态” 的端到端生成，其核心能力体现在以下几个方面：</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13624f34-713b-469f-9029-9de52bf08e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503761802\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13624f34-713b-469f-9029-9de52bf08e00/public\">\n   </section>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">机器人动作与像素的高精度对齐：将机械臂 6D 位姿（x,y,z,roll,pitch,yaw）与末端执行器行程投影为 action map，确保物理动作与图像帧的像素级对齐，精准建模 “抓取”、“放置”、“碰撞”、“推拉”、“快速抛掷”、“缓慢摇晃” 等复杂动力学行为；</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">动态多视图建模：引入 Ray Map 编码相机运动轨迹，支持头部 、腕部等多视角协同生成一致且连贯的视觉场景，赋予机器人更全面的环境生成能力。；</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">卓越的长时序一致性：采用 Chunk-Wise 自回归扩散架构与稀疏记忆机制（Sparse Memory），EVAC 能够实现单视图稳定生成长达 30 个连续片段、多视图下亦可维持 10 个连续片段的无漂移稳定输出，保证了模拟过程在时间轴上的连贯性与真实性；</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">数据高效利用：融合 Agibot-World 数据集 + 失败轨迹（如抓取滑脱、路径碰撞）提升生成质量，该策略能有效抑制幻觉现象，使模型能更合理、更全面地建模机器人与环境的交互动态。</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfe9f80e-6c39-4a47-f419-14a51e7cb700/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">生成式仿真评估 + 数据引擎双轮驱动</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503761798\" data-ratio=\"0.3917525773195876\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4536f26-7791-4a0f-80f8-6459306a5000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"582\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4536f26-7791-4a0f-80f8-6459306a5000/public\">\n   </section>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">生成式仿真评测</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对真机评测成本高、风险大、难以复现等痛点，EVAC 开创性地提出了生成式模拟评测方案，它能与待评测的策略模型进行交替推理，构建起一套完整的交互式评测管线。实验显示，在多个任务中，EVAC 所生成的评测结果与真机评测的成功率具有高度一致性，甚至能够可靠地识别出性能更优的模型权重，大幅提升了策略模型的筛选效率。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503761801\" data-ratio=\"0.3115942028985507\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbab10e4-2603-4718-9dc0-725a59d1c400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbab10e4-2603-4718-9dc0-725a59d1c400/public\">\n   </section>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">数据增广引擎</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EVAC 能够基于极少量的专家轨迹数据，通过动作插值与高保真画面生成技术进行大规模数据增广。应用结果表明，采用 EVAC 数据增广数据训练的策略模型，其任务成功率提升高达 29%，目标跟随性得到显著改善，验证了这一方案在具身智能研究中的实用性与高性价比。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbab10e4-2603-4718-9dc0-725a59d1c400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3115942028985507\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503761800\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbab10e4-2603-4718-9dc0-725a59d1c400/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/313e2e4c-d404-46e9-1145-eaf024e34100/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">打造具身世界模型的 “质检尺”</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了科学、系统地衡量具身世界模型的性能表现，智元机器人推出了全球首个具身世界模型评测基准——EWMBench，旨在填补行业空白，构建统一、可信的评测标准。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503761807\" data-ratio=\"0.2898550724637681\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/38a6d5d6-91fd-4f74-2de0-655efe593100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/38a6d5d6-91fd-4f74-2de0-655efe593100/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfe9f80e-6c39-4a47-f419-14a51e7cb700/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">三维度评估体系：场景 × 动作 × 语义的立体考核</span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对机器人操作场景的复杂性与特殊性，EWMBench 构建了立体化的评估体系，从场景一致性、动作合理性 与 语义对齐与多样性 三大核心指标进行分析：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">场景一致性 Scene Consistency，评估生成场景中背景 / 物体 / 视角等稳固度与真实性，采用微调过的 DINOv2 特征进行量化。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">动作合理性 Motion Correctness，利用 HSD (Symmetric Hausdorff Distance), nDTW (normalized Dynamic Time Warping) 和 Dynamics Score 三重互补指标协同精确评估生成动作的合理性与动力学真实度。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">语义对齐与多样性 Semantic Alignment &amp; Diversity，结合 MLLM(多模态大模型）和 CLIP 从全局指令对齐度、关键步骤语义准确性、逻辑合理性等多个层次对生成视频进行语义理解评估。</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503761808\" data-ratio=\"0.35507246376811596\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c9c597a-5c32-462a-65fc-1de603d04c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c9c597a-5c32-462a-65fc-1de603d04c00/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfe9f80e-6c39-4a47-f419-14a51e7cb700/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">权威数据支撑与便捷开源工具</span>\n   </section>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">基准数据集：EWMBench 基于行业领先的开源百万真机数据集 AgiBot World 构建，涵盖了家居、工业、医疗三大场景的 10 类典型机器人操作任务和刚体 / 柔体 / 流体 / 关节物体等多种交互对象，其中包含超过 300 个精心设计的测试样本及 30% 挑战性场景（低光照 / 部分遮挡），全面验证模型在复杂环境下的鲁棒性。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <section>\n      <span leaf=\"\">开源评测工具：智元机器人同步开源了全流程评测工具，支持一键生成标准化对比报告，大幅降低评估门槛，方便研究者快速开展模型比较与性能分析，加速实验验证与成果复现。</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n    <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cfe9f80e-6c39-4a47-f419-14a51e7cb700/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">卓越评测性能：更贴近人类主观感知</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/67b1d6e8-2598-4480-c5d7-05fe56636300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24154589371980675\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503761806\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/67b1d6e8-2598-4480-c5d7-05fe56636300/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">相较于当前主流视频生成评测基准 VBench，EWMBench 在评测结果与人类主观判断的一致性方面表现更优，能够更真实、细致地反映具身世界模型在交互理解、动作还原与视觉一致性等核心维度的实际能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">EnerVerse 作为强大的世界模型基础架构，为 EVAC 提供可靠的基础框架与预训练能力，而 EVAC 生成的多样化高质量数据又能反哺 EnerVerse 模型的持续优化，二者形成 “训练 - 验证” 技术闭环，不断推动模型性能突破。通过 EWMBench 提供的精细化、多维度量化分析，研发团队可以精准定位 EVAC 在处理如 “多物体交互”“动态环境避障” 等复杂场景的潜在不足，从而进行更具针对性的优化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">据悉，EVAC 与 EWMBench 组合方案，已正式入选 AgiBot World Challenge @ IROS 2025 – World Model 赛道的官方基线系统与评测标准。</span></p>\n   <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-we